_sText:
This is my retexture of gg_lego_arena by mck-76.
The textures on the original were absolutely horrible, so I redid it with the amazing lego textures made by boharox. I also made some minor structural changes for visual improvement.

Custom textures and nav file packed into the bsp using pakrat, bzip file included for servers with fastdl. 

Pleaes note that I have suspended work on my maps for the time being, this is taken AS-IS. I know it has a couple of texture errors but Its nothing you can't live with.
